description:
The Pirate, last years Champion, does not even break a sweat as she smashes the record for most points scored in a match. Justine Joli is a lover not a fighter. The problem is that when J.J is getting fingered, she likes it too much. And that doesn't help her, because super horny nymphos do not do well at US. Not that there is anything wrong with that!
WEEKEND, EXTRA, BONUS UPDATE.
title: The Pirate (10-1)
